                  We migrated 300–400 employees from FortiGate and saw immediate gains in speed, security, and user experience, all at a lower cost.
                </blockquote>
                <div class="why-section-testimonial__attr">
                  <img src="/images/data/testimonials/dext-by-iris.png" alt="Dext by Iris" width="100" height="28" />
                  <span>Dimitar D., Director of IT Infrastructure</span>
                  <a href="https://www.capterra.com/p/10034288/Defguard/#Capterra___7078107/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="why-section-testimonial__capterra">Read full review on Capterra</a>
