          <p>Defguard delivers what legacy appliances cannot: a secure, modern VPN platform built for today's threat landscape.</p>
          <FeatureCapsules
            features={[
              {
                title: "Secured control-plane",
                description: "Control plane isolated from the Internet—business logic and connection management stay inside your network. No single point of failure like FortiGate's monolithic appliance.",
